  "wechat_html": "<img src='https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/3hAJnwuyZuicicZkgJBUCCaricdibomDBrTzXgUR7FJnf11qGIo8nmKt6RxibXrb5s4RFb9UZ9UOHQy7fqQyI377Licw/0?wx_fmt=gif' style='width:100%;display:block;'><section style='padding:0;'><section style=\"margin:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#f6efe4 0%,#fbf8f2 58%,#ffffff 100%);padding:1px;color:#1f2937;\"><section style=\"width:100%;margin:0;\"><section style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);border:1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.16);box-shadow:0 12px 28px rgba(15,23,42,0.06);border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:relative;background:#d6d3d1;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-15/hf-event-00.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;display:block;\"></div><section style=\"padding:16px 12px 10px;\"><div style=\"display:inline-block;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:999px;background:#111827;color:#f9fafb;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;\">History Today</div><h1 style=\"font-size:29px;line-height:1.22;margin:12px 0 10px;color:#111827;font-family:Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif;\">历史上的今天：公历日期的奥秘</h1><p style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;color:#475569;margin:0;\">探索公历日期背后的时间流逝与历法常识。</p></section><section style=\"padding:0 10px 12px;\"><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">在漫长的历史长河中，每一天都有其独特的坐标。当我们翻开日历，3月15日这一天在公历中占据着特定的位置。对于平年而言，它是全年中的第74天，而对于闰年，则是第75天。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-15/hf-event-01.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">时间的流逝总是悄无声息。每年的这一天，不仅是日历上的一个数字，它还提醒着我们距离年底还有多少时光。平年余下291天，而闰年则余下290天，这种精确的计算构成了我们现代生活的基础。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-15/hf-event-02.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">历法的演变是人类文明智慧的结晶。从古至今，人们通过观测天体运行来制定规则，使得社会生活能够井然有序地进行。这种对时间的精准把握，是科学进步的重要体现。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-15/hf-event-03.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">回顾历史，我们常常感叹时间的飞逝。无论是在哪个季节，每一个日期都承载着特定的天数意义。通过了解这些基础的时间知识，我们能更清晰地感受时间流动的节奏。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-15/hf-event-04.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div><div style=\"background:#fffdf8;border:1px solid rgba(226,232,240,0.88);border-radius:16px;padding:14px 12px;margin:0 0 12px;box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.035);\"><p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.92;margin:0;color:#334155;\">历史不仅是大事的记录，也是这些细微时间节点的堆叠。让我们在每一个平凡的日子里，珍惜当下，感受时间赋予生活的独特韵律与意义。</p></div><div style=\"margin:0 0 14px;\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/duguBoss/daily-history-hub/main/assets/generated/history_today/2026-03-15/hf-event-05.png\" style=\"width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;border-radius:16px;display:block;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(15,23,42,0.08);\"></div></section></section></section></section></section><img src='https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/3hAJnwuyZuicicZkgJBUCCaricdibomDBrTzk57DCmhVC16o9ILH0Tn1YPEiarfLRRQSVFN2mJdeYibGnBPialPIzvojw/0?wx_fmt=gif' style='width:100%;display:block;'>"
